N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 16 ยง 255.733 - Compressor stations: isolation of equipment for maintenance or alterations

State Regulations

Each operator shall establish procedures for maintaining
compressor stations, including provisions for isolating units or sections of
pipe and for purging before returning to service. Notes
